	(lib_symbols)
	(text "MCU  (RP2040 control / supervision)
Components:
 - U: RP2040 (QFN-56)  + 12MHz xtal
 - U: W25Q128 QSPI flash (SOIC-8)
 - J: USB-C (flash UF2 + serial)
 - SW: BOOTSEL, RUN buttons ; rate-select DIP
 - LEDs: EXT-LOCK / INT-MASTER / FAULT
I2C0 -> CS2000 (SDA/SCL).  SPI0 -> DIT4192 (SCK/MOSI/CS).
Reads WCLK_MON (PIO freq count) + CS2K_UNLK.  Drives CONV_RST_N.
USB_VBUS -> Power sheet (OR diode).  See aes-adc-firmware.md"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
